# Environment Variables Example File
# Rename this file from .env.example to .env and fill in your keys.

# Your Paystack Public Key
VITE_PAYSTACK_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Important warnings:
# 1. Do NOT put your Paystack SECRET key here. It is for backend use only!
# 2. Make sure .env is added to your .gitignore so you don't commit it to GitHub.
